<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto my-12 px-6 flex-grow">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-150 p-6 sm:p-10 relative overflow-hidden">
    
    <!-- Top Decorative Gradient Line -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-blue-600"></div>

    <!-- Header title -->
    <div class="border-b border-gray-150 pb-6 mb-8 text-center sm:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold font-display text-gray-950 tracking-tight flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start">
        <i data-lucide="file-text" class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-teal-600"></i> Conditions of Use
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Last Updated: June 2026. Please read these Terms of Use carefully before using our platform.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid Layout -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Quick Navigation Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-5 rounded-2xl sticky top-6">
          <h4 class="font-extrabold text-sm text-gray-950 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2 mb-3">Quick Navigation</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs text-teal-700 font-medium">
            <li><a href="#welcome" class="hover:underline flex items-center"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5"></i> 1. Welcome to Shopzy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#account" class="hover:underline flex items-center"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5"></i> 2. Your Account & Security</a></li>
            <li><a href="#privacy" class="hover:underline flex items-center"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5"></i> 3. Privacy & Integrity</a></li>
            <li><a href="#products" class="hover:underline flex items-center"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5"></i> 4. Products & Pricing</a></li>
            <li><a href="#liability" class="hover:underline flex items-center"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5"></i> 5. Limitation of Liability</a></li>
            <li><a href="#governing" class="hover:underline flex items-center"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5"></i> 6. Governing Law</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Legal Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-sans">
        
        <section id="welcome" class="scroll-mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-950 mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded mr-2">Sec. 1</span> Welcome to Shopzy
          </h3>
          <p>
            Welcome to Shopzy! Shopzy provides its services to you subject to the notices, terms, and conditions set forth in this agreement. By accessing, browsing, or using this website, you agree to be bound by all the terms of use outlined herein.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">
            We reserve the right to change this Site and these terms at any time. Any changes will be posted here and your continued usage indicates your acceptance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="account" class="scroll-mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-950 mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded mr-2">Sec. 2</span> Your Account & Security
          </h3>
          <p>
            If you create an account on Shopzy, you are solely responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials, login passwords, and restriction of unauthorized access to your computer/devices. You agree to accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your account.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We reserve the right to refuse service, terminate accounts, remove or edit content, or cancel orders in our sole discretion if we suspect fraudulent or malicious behaviour.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="privacy" class="scroll-mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-950 mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded mr-2">Sec. 3</span> Privacy & Integrity
          </h3>
          <p>
            Our relationship complies with modern data ethics. Your privacy is paramount; please review our <a href="/privacy-notice" class="text-blue-600 underline font-medium">Privacy Notice</a>, which also governs your visit to Shopzy, to understand our guidelines and operations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="products" class="scroll-mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-950 mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded mr-2">Sec. 4</span> Products & Pricing
          </h3>
          <p>
            We strive to display our products, specifications, images, and prices as accurately as humanly possible. However, we do not warrant that product descriptions or other site content are 100% error-free. 
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">
            In the event that a product is listed at an incorrect price due to transactional bugs, we reserve the right to refuse or cancel any orders placed for that product.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="liability" class="scroll-mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-950 mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded mr-2">Sec. 5</span> Limitation of Liability
          </h3>
          <p>
            This site is provided by Shopzy on an "As Is" and "As Available" basis. Shopzy makes no representations or warranties of any kind, express or implied, as to the operation of this site, the accuracy of its information, contents, or products.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="governing" class="scroll-mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-950 mb-3 flex items-center">
            <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded mr-2">Sec. 6</span> Governing Law
          </h3>
          <p>
            By visiting Shopzy, you agree that the local and national digital statutes, without regard to principles of conflict of laws, will govern these Conditions of Use and any dispute that might arise between you and Shopzy.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
